{
  "texts": [
    "In other words, there is no gold standard labels provided by human professionals assessing degree expressions proficiency.",
    "Therefore, we took Writing_Sample (overall essay score rated by domain experts) as the gold standard label and as a proxy of degree expressions proficiency, and we made the assumption that a good essay score (a high Writing_Sample score) is an indicator of learners' general mastery of different language phenomena in the target language, possibly including degree expressions.",
    "First, we compared efficacy of LLMs-surprisals with the classic cohesion indices.",
    "Specifically, the two proficiency classes were set based on the median of the variable Writing_Sample.",
    "Data with a Writing_Sample score 3.3 or higher is labeled as high degree expressions proficiency otherwise as low."
  ]
}